    <stitle>530 and DT-466/408 Diesel Engine Service (1994) - VIBRATION DAMPER, CRANKSHAFT, MAIN BEARINGS, FLYWHEEL AND
        CRANKCASE - FLYWHEEL - INSPECTION
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="2">
        <title>INSPECTION</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Visually inspect the flywheel for cracks, heat checks and extensive scoring which would make
                it unfit for further service. Replace or resurface as required.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect the ring gear for worn, chipped or cracked teeth. If teeth are damaged, replace the
                ring gear.
            </para>
